The paper deals with image-to-image translation, which is a topic closely related to computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves the use of a self-inverse function, which is a concept that falls under the umbrella of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of generative adversarial networks (GANs), which is a popular technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the experiments involve the use of datasets and evaluation metrics commonly used in computer graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
